# ─── Cloudflare Pages _redirects ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# SETUP REQUIRED: Replace every instance of https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app
# with your actual Railway deployment URL before deploying.
# Example: https://gmt-production.up.railway.app
#
# This file proxies all /api/* requests to the Railway backend at the
# Cloudflare edge so the browser never exposes the Railway URL.
# The /* catch-all at the bottom enables React Router client-side routing.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# GMT API proxy rules — all /api/* traffic forwarded to Railway backend
# RAILWAY_BACKEND is set as an environment variable in Cloudflare Pages dashboard
# Format: /api/path/*  https://your-app.up.railway.app/api/path/:splat  200

/api/v1/*           https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app/api/v1/:splat           200
/api/yahoo/*        https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app/api/yahoo/:splat        200
/api/finnhub/*      https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app/api/finnhub/:splat      200
/api/alphavantage/* https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app/api/alphavantage/:splat 200
/api/fred/*         https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app/api/fred/:splat         200
/api/coingecko/*    https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app/api/coingecko/:splat    200
/api/fmp/*          https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app/api/fmp/*               200
/api/brapi/*        https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app/api/brapi/:splat        200
/api/bcb/*          https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app/api/bcb/:splat          200
/api/awesomeapi/*   https://global-markets-terminal.up.railway.app/api/awesomeapi/:splat   200

# SPA catch-all — serve index.html for all unmatched routes (React Router)
/*                  /index.html                                       200
